These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, lily
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person who growszinnia##1
2. the person who growslily is between the fan of pop and the person who growszinnia##2
3. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Flower      | zinnia | lily | azalea |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, avocado, potato
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the person eating lettuce##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Food   | lettuce    | potato        | avocado |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, roller, quad-bike
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the owner of the ferret and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Transport   | roller | scooter     | quad-bike |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing  | sudoku     | card-games |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, disco, house
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of house is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | house     | classical |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, cranberry, broccoli
1. the person eating pineapple is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person eating cranberry##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Food         | cranberry | pineapple | broccoli |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, car, ship
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person driving the bike is between the person eating pineapple and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Transport   | car | bike | ship     |

