.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
City: hannover, paris, marseilles
1. the person watching satire movies is the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to paris is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| City   | hannover | paris | marseilles |

 #################################

 
