.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
City: paris, hamburg, hannover
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| City   | hamburg | paris      | hannover      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

