.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, rock, salsa
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, zombie, western
1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie | western | crime |

